fields.description:
pyarrow.create_library_symlinks() doesn't create symlink on macos.

```

def get_symlink_path(hard_path):
  return '.'.join((hard_path.split('.')[0], 'dylib'))

```

should be changed to

```

def get_symlink_path(hard_path):
  splits = hard_path.split('.')
  splits.pop(-2)
  return '.'.join(splits)

```
